name: searx
full_description:
Searx is a privacy-respecting metasearch engine, aggregating the results of other search engines while not storing information about its users. 

For an easy to install, battery included setup: https://github.com/searx/searx-docker (include this image, [Filtron](https://github.com/asciimoo/searx/issues/1228), [Morty](https://github.com/asciimoo/searx/issues/1228) and [searx-checker](https://github.com/searx/searx-checker))

For more details, see https://searx.github.io/searx/admin/installation-docker.html

This image is built using travis: https://travis-ci.org/searx/searx  ([Dockerfile](https://github.com/searx/searx/blob/master/Dockerfile) and [sh script](https://github.com/asciimoo/searx/blob/master/manage.sh#L162))

Source code: https://github.com/searx/searx
